    <h2 class="text-center">How it’s made, from the kitchen to your plate</h2>
    <p>
      Shortie works by leveraging a type of generative AI – a large language
      model (LLM) – in the background. An email invitation from the organizer
      prompts you to join a group order, telling you to view the preselected
      menu and choose a meal. Once you navigate to the menu, Shortie is
      comparing your dietary preferences and past orders and to all of the
      ingredients on the menu. It then ranks the meals, putting the best fit at
      the top.
    </p>
