      Additionally, Shortie is reading the menu and breaking all of the meals
      into categories. Then, it’s generating questions for you to help guide
      your decision-making process. Yes, that’s right -- the LLM is asking the
      user questions, and remembering the answers to the previous questions.You
      should see the menu items being re-ranked according to your answers to
      those questions.
    </p>
